reviewText:
I give this a 4/5 because some season and movie had really bad English subtitles. It was hard to follow the dialogue. Otherwise it would of been a 5/5. Delivery was fast and packaging was great.

If any of you grew up watching your favorite heroes like power rangers or even those super heroes from DC and Marvel, then check out Garo. However, be warned its not for little children as there is nudity, blood, and foul language. I just want to say, Check it out on YouTube first to see if its something youll enjoy watching before buying!
Came fast and as described! Thanks Beverly!
